00:05:15.180 --> 00:05:19.650
Anyway, you see this bunny eat this bowl,
but this is done by a student

00:05:19.650 --> 00:05:21.400
developer using the Mac platform.

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:22.840
This is only on the Mac.

00:05:22.840 --> 00:05:25.520
And these guys have a great
student effort going on there,

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:27.770
and I think it's just one of
many going around the world.

00:05:27.940 --> 00:05:30.550
And I'll tell you,
the coolest experience I had was about

00:05:30.550 --> 00:05:32.820
now about two and a half years ago.

00:05:32.820 --> 00:05:34.640
I was at this university.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:36.780
And these guys have these
great labs out there.

00:05:36.780 --> 00:05:39.010
You know, they have a Mac lab,
they have a Windows lab,

00:05:39.020 --> 00:05:40.320
and they have a Unix lab.

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:44.040
