"Man, the Mac lab is the most popular

00:05:44.090 --> 00:05:46.730
on campus." Now for background,
there's not a lot of

00:05:46.730 --> 00:05:47.860
Macs in China right now.

00:05:47.860 --> 00:05:50.520
