00:47:28.520 --> 00:47:32.050
With World of Warcraft in a large
outdoor scene on a mountaintop spinning

00:47:32.100 --> 00:47:34.930
around where you see the mountain
ranges and you see all the trees and

00:47:34.930 --> 00:47:40.300
it's pretty geometrically complicated,
you go from 68 to 132 frames per second.

00:47:40.300 --> 00:47:43.250
So this is the type of performance you
can get with our new multi-threaded

00:47:43.350 --> 00:47:46.890
OpenGL stack in MacÂ OSÂ X Leopard.

00:47:47.590 --> 00:47:50.680
Now, obviously if you're here, you know,
